| **Server fingerprint** | `X-Powered-By: Express` exposed | Disabled |
| **Rate limiting** | None | 100 req/15 min per IP |
| **Body parsing** | Not configured | JSON + URL-encoded with 10kb size cap |
| **Input validation** | None | Rejects unexpected query params |
| **404 handling** | Express default (HTML) | JSON-consistent `{ error: "Not Found" }` |
| **Error handling** | None (stack trace leak) | Global handler; detail only in dev mode |
